      <title>若获得投资，英国石油产量或将超过预期 30%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/uk-could-beat-oil-output-forecast-by-30-if-investment-secured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[某行业组织表示，如果能获得约 200 亿英镑的新投资，到本世纪末，英国的石油和天然气产量可能比目前预计的多出近 30%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/uk-could-beat-oil-output-forecast-by-30-if-investment-secured</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
